rComments: He is very helpful and does a lot of examples in class on Fridays. Also a nice (and hot) TA. His sensible haircut and Austrian accent kept me coming back...:-)

AWESOME TA!!!  Quizzes are very fair, attendance policy fair.  Gives really helpful handouts, has a website to ask questions if you're out of class, will meet outside of office hours. Overall and awesome guy - and hot! :)
